#: ../../S/sunspots.rst:5
msgid "sunspots"
msgstr "sunspots"

#: ../../S/sunspots.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../S/sunspots.rst:10
msgid ""
"Notional cause of an odd error. \"Why did the program suddenly turn the "
"screen blue?\" \"Sunspots, I guess.\""
msgstr "奇妙なエラーの想定上の原因。「なぜプログラムが突然画面を青くしたんだ?」「太陽の黒点だろう。」"

#: ../../S/sunspots.rst:15
msgid ""
"Also the cause of :ref:`bit-rot` — from the myth that sunspots will increase"
" :ref:`cosmic-rays`\\, which can flip single bits in memory. See also "
":ref:`phase-of-the-moon`\\."
msgstr ""
":ref:`bit-rot`\\ の原因でもある——太陽の黒点が\\ :ref:`cosmic-rays`\\ "
"を増やし、それがメモリの単一ビットを反転させうるという俗説から。\\ :ref:`phase-of-the-moon`\\ も参照。"
